5. Design Features
5.1 Typography
The website uses the Lexend font family throughout, chosen for its excellent readability and modern appearance.

Headings: Lexend 600-700 weight for impact
Body Text: Lexend 300-400 weight for readability
Line Height: 1.7-1.8 for optimal reading comfort
Font Sizes: Responsive scaling from mobile to desktop
5.2 Color Palette
Color	Hex Code	Usage
Primary Black	#000000	Navigation gradients, emphasis
Secondary Dark	#2d3436	Headers, buttons, accents
Text Primary	#1a1a1a	Main headings and important text
Text Secondary	#555555